text: New curry rice stall in the area, the vegetables were really tasty and the braised pork was soft and full of flavour. The sambal chilli is also really awesome and it really packs a punch.
Ordered curry rice takeaway and no curry sauce was given at all (the bit of gravy on the rice are just from the dishes). Huge disappointment to have curry rice without curry.
Must try the sweet and sour pork. During lunch. Spot on!
Tasty and value for money. Will be back
